{"tid":1673373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好睇小今晚加泰集會","createTime":"2019-10-24T15:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T13:39:16.000Z","uid":279401,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"22f4a1c762a54a489ae257c6998657c6ef91f0c4","tid":1673373,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"同你回帶中共點樣由各國商家影響返其國家！<br />\n<br />\n90年代尾，中共係國際舞臺仲係冇咩話語權，係2001年，佢地成立博鰲亞洲論壇，初期好多國家都唔會派員出席(現實當時係國際上冇咩面) 所以佢地就主要邀請商人宣傳內地商機，利用影響商人對大陸睇法而由商家再影響其國家一步步移向大陸&hellip;&hellip;18年後既博鰲論壇已經係大部份國家都會出席既論壇，一帶一路就係咁吹下吹下出黎&hellip;&hellip;唔詳細講浪費大家青春！<br />\n<br />\n我地係弱勢既一方，冇國家力量支持，要走落去除左過去和理非道德感召，令國際幫香港人一D口頭支持，其實只係面對一步又一步既壓迫，冇實際得到過野！抗爭必須要再進化，唔好睇小今日加泰嗰小小人，依個係國際上既一個鐘聲，去到依家見到攬炒到和你Shop到爆買下一步就係要創造更多價值同效益，談判一定要有野係手對方先會同你交換！唔好諗住講就會俾野你，回歸到依家實際只係得到負數，由依家開始一步步要進化除左抗爭行動外，要去建立經濟能力！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8D%9A%E9%B3%8C%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E8%AE%BA%E5%9D%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%258D%259A%25E9%25B3%258C%25E4%25BA%259A%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25AE%25BA%25E5%259D%259B&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=08727628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8D%9A%E9%B3%8C%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E8%AE%BA%E5%9D%9B</a><br />\n<br />\n先講到依度<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力！<br />\n五大訴求， 缺一不可"},{"pid":"aec9613c8591a8522a42666e5e6701cbaa8192c2","tid":1673373,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Sw3aYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Sw3aYY.jpg&h=18631120&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4f8d3466e35069947147525037e4e3d1349978f2","tid":1673373,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:29:27.000Z","msg":"早幾日吹完反加泰集會風，今晚就開始吹恥笑早幾日反加泰集會嘅風<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673275</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dde980dc7b3a861b8c8513e4f138f4a3c64dc2e7","tid":1673373,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"手殘，幫你推返3次"},{"pid":"7a36b1ababa35ee24c7063ea562ca49c7489e873","tid":1673373,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"推 1/3"},{"pid":"cc98482ad709a50c2bcc720e625017c2ea0d3b92","tid":1673373,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"539397f436f9df080511d6eae768a0416dd90b93","tid":1673373,"uid":194143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:51:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4701865cc4da5e4a8b7654754bcd3cad5d7d3b69","tid":1673373,"uid":22741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:22:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a241fc96d9a1ab34e22154077f358a61bf2b67d","tid":1673373,"uid":2900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:53:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d860cd28e2ac59cd5fe1c6b6b014ae57221f331c","tid":1673373,"uid":22741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:06:31.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"db8c1f68f28aeffd47454e7e6b2bceffc08c9ae6","tid":1673373,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"googogogood"}]}